OL,3,CFamily of soldier missing for a month
OL,4,Cspeak of devastation
OL,6,FThe family of a soldier who has been
OL,7,Fmissing from his barracks for a month
OL,8,Fhave spoken of their devastation.
OL,10,FL Cpl Ryan Rudd, 28, has not been seen
OL,11,Fsince he left Catterick Garrison,
OL,12,FNorth Yorkshire, for a night out with
OL,13,Ffriends in Selby on Valentine's Day.
OL,15,FNorth Yorkshire Police say the last
OL,16,Fconfirmed sighting was at 2.54am on 15
OL,17,FFebruary as he walked past the Old
OL,18,FFlour factory towards New Millgate.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/5
