PN,36902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1773667698
OL,3,CFamily of soldier missing for a month
OL,4,Cspeak of devastation
OL,6,FL Cpl Rudd's parents Kerstin and Ken
OL,7,Fsaid in a statement: "As a family, we
OL,8,Fare devastated and struggling to put
OL,9,Finto words how we feel.
OL,11,F"We would ask anyone who has even the
OL,12,Fsmallest piece of information that
OL,13,Fcould help bring Ryan home to please
OL,14,Fcontact the police. We are desperate
OL,15,Fto have him back."
OL,26,@oD@VOUsD@AOUwD@RO]
