PN,36903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1773667698
OL,3,CFamily of soldier missing for a month
OL,4,Cspeak of devastation
OL,6,FIt is understood L Cpl Rudd, a member
OL,7,Fof 1st Battalion, Royal Yorkshire
OL,8,FRegiment, was not on annual leave at
OL,9,Fthe time he disappeared and was
OL,10,Fexpected on duty 24 hours after he was
OL,11,Flast seen.
OL,13,FNorth Yorkshire Police was not
OL,14,Finformed until 1 March.
OL,16,FThe MoD has previously said it is
OL,17,Finvestigating why his absence was not
OL,18,Freported earlier.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/5
