PN,36904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1773667698
OL,3,CFamily of soldier missing for a month
OL,4,Cspeak of devastation
OL,6,FPolice say they have carried out
OL,7,Fdetailed enquiries including CCTV
OL,8,Ftrawls and have spoken to residents.
OL,10,FThey have also searched the nearby
OL,11,Fcountryside and water using specialist
OL,12,Fequipment and drones.
OL,14,FInsp Ciaran Conlon said: "This is an
OL,15,Fextremely difficult time for Ryan's
OL,16,Ffamily, and they are currently
OL,17,Freceiving support from specialist
OL,18,Fofficers.
OL,26,@vD@ZOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/5
