FL,370,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1773667698
OL,3,CFamily of soldier missing for a month
OL,4,Cspeak of devastation
OL,6,F"As with any investigation, we remain
OL,7,Fopen minded and will continue to
OL,8,Fexplore all lines of enquiry, but we
OL,9,Fmust accept the possibility that Ryan
OL,10,Fhas entered the River Ouse."
OL,12,FL Cpl Rudd is described as white,
OL,13,Faround 5ft 8in tall and slim with dark
OL,14,Fbrown hair.
